description: Deal Blabs lists coupons and promos
overview: At Dealblabs.com coupon and promo codes are listed from trusted online retailers. For example you will find coupons for Newegg, Dell, Sephora, Macys, BestBuy, Target, Walmart and promodes for many others. Coupons are verified by the support team but also can be submitted by the user community that is currently being built. In this economy savings are important, so is deals and coupons accuracy, Dealblabs.com verifies the discount information before delivering it to consumers.
